{"tid":2181244,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"業主趕住移民 東環兩房蝕讓100萬元出貨","createTime":"2020-08-30T12:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T00:44:06.000Z","uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cd4f3ecf2e396e0a0b7e3ef20db4cb200408b3b9","tid":2181244,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T12:40:00.000Z","msg":"業主賣樓移民，因單位未過3年，東涌東環2房業主要付SSD，兼蝕賣單位，料損失約百萬元。市場人士指，東涌東環1B座低層9室，實用面積484平方呎，2房間隔，以610萬元易手，實用呎價12,603元。<br />\n原業主於2019年以650萬元購入，帳面已蝕40萬元，因單位未過3年SSD，業主要付SSD（約1成樓價，即61萬元），連同帳面蝕價，以及其他釐印費、律師費等費用，實際損失約百萬元。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，上月同座同室高兩層單位以660萬元沽出，意味剛易手造價低於市場價。"},{"pid":"36e76249149fe073375cfeb538820b3b79947844","tid":2181244,"uid":361751,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T12:50:52.000Z","msg":"郊區<br />\n<br />\n唔計"},{"pid":"a0f45923ac443a8fa51a4f27bbf9c0e4c57331cb","tid":2181244,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T12:58:55.000Z","msg":"蝕過百萬咁走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a75db06105cd422708b09e56c0b393ebc8f8203","tid":2181244,"uid":38626,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:02:20.000Z","msg":"再遲啲，蝕更多"},{"pid":"17357464f2991ddf73dae3706cdd55c7bc5cc23d","tid":2181244,"uid":196420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T00:44:06.000Z","msg":"移民唔會賣樓<br />\nFake news"}]}